          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "desc": "A jade piece which, despite its exquisite packaging, has been placed in one of the least prominent positions in the store.</br>The box comes with an official-looking certificate of premium quality, issued by an organization that no one has ever heard of.</br>To the untrained eye, the luxurious packaging and accessories would probably be enough to lure one in.</br>However, it is still reasonable value for money when compared with genuine top-quality jade pieces.</br>",
